title: Week 4 Recap: The Eagles Are in First Place, the Texans Are Dead, and Listener Questions | The Ringer NFL Show
description:
Kevin Clark and Nora Princiotti discuss the Philadelphia Eagles moving into first place in the NFC East (5:07), and the Dallas Cowboys losing again despite another big performance from Dak Prescott (11:31). Then they pick their Week 4 winners and losers (45:43) and answer a few listener questions (01:23:21). 

Host: Kevin Clark and Nora Princiotti
